    <id>mxmlscores</id>
    <name>Scores</name>
    <summary>Display and play MusicXML files with OpenSheetMusicDisplay</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
Scores allows you to display, play, and share musical scores in MusicXML and other formats directly in Nextcloud.

Features:
- Display MusicXML, MusicXML compressed (MXL), and other sheet music formats
- Interactive playback with tempo and volume control
- Navigate through measures with keyboard shortcuts
- Zoom in/out for better readability
- Loop playback for practice
- Full integration with Nextcloud Files
- Public sharing with read-only access
- Support for Guitar Pro and MEI formats

Powered by OpenSheetMusicDisplay library.
    ]]></description>
